'''单环刺螠'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Urechis unicinctus''}}）是一种海生的[[螠虫动物門|螠虫动物]]，俗称'''海肠'''，[[胶东半岛|胶东半岛]]又称'''海雞子'''或'''海牛子'''，英文俗名為'''陰莖魚'''（{{lang|en|penis fish}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/E0AD99|title=UFE - Fibrinolytic enzyme - Urechis unicinctus (Fat innkeeper worm) - UFE gene & protein|website=www.uniprot.org|access-date=2019-12-16|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423130124/https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/E0AD99|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Gong/>），因其形似[[男性生殖器官|男性生殖器官]][[陰莖|陰莖]]而得名。分布於北美洲西岸的同屬物種{{le|美洲刺螠|Urechis caupo}}也有此別稱<ref name=WallaWalla>{{cite web|url = https://inverts.wallawalla.edu/Echiura/Urechis_caupo.html|title = ''Urechis caupo'' Fisher and MacGinitie, 1928|work = Invertebrates of the Salish Sea|last = Cowles|first = Dave|year = 2010|publisher = Rosario Beach Marine Laboratory (a campus of [[Walla_Walla_University|Walla Walla University]], Washington)|access-date = 25 January 2019|archive-date = 2019-12-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191213184615/https://inverts.wallawalla.edu/Echiura/Urechis_caupo.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==生態 == 
单环刺螠和其他{{le|刺螠科|Urechidae}}物種一樣是生活在海边[[潮間帶|潮間帶]]泥性底質或[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]區<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lunwentianxia.com/product.sf.3358610.1/|title=单环刺螠（Urechis unicinctus）vasa基因及β-actin基因的克隆与表达分析|language=zh-cn|access-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121118192252/http://lunwentianxia.com/product.sf.3358610.1/|archive-date=2012-11-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，這種動物體型肥大，身體前端具一長吻用於覓食，極具彈性，可伸長至一公尺以上，利用其黏性黏著底部的小動物或有機顆粒，由於吻部在外覓食而容易被[[海鳥|海鳥]]啄食，而再生性極強。棲息於泥灘的单环刺螠有很好的潛沙能力，身體能潛到40公分以上<ref name="paper">{{cite journal|url=http://web2.nmns.edu.tw/PubLib/NewsLetter/98/260/a-3.pdf|title=奇特的海鮮－特殊的食用海洋無脊椎動物|author=[[李坤瑄|李坤瑄]]|journal=國立自然科學博物館館訊|volume=第260期|language=zh-hant|access-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509033124/http://web2.nmns.edu.tw/PubLib/NewsLetter/98/260/a-3.pdf|archive-date=2016-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，棲息於基質的洞中濾食，有助於減少海水基質的污染。单环刺螠會被許多{{le|底棲魚類|groundfish}}捕食，其棲息的洞中可能有[[巴氏無齒蟹|巴氏無齒蟹]]、''{{tsl|nl|Pseudopinnixa carinata}}''等[[片利共生|片利共生]]的小型螃蟹<ref name="pmid24698400"/><ref>{{cite journal|title=Macrofauna Associated with Echiuran Burrows: A Review with New Observations of the Innkeeper Worm, Ochetostoma erythrogrammon Leuckart and Rüppel, in Venezuela|author=Arthur Anker, Galena-Vantsetti Murina, Carlos Lira, Jonathan A. Vera Caripe, A. Richard Palmer, Ming-Shiou Jeng|journal=Zoological Studies|volume=44|issue=2|page=157-190|year=2005|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/215621978_Macrofauna_Associated_with_Echiuran_Burrows_A_Review_with_New_Observations_of_the_Innkeeper_Worm_Ochetostoma_erythrogrammon_Leuckart_and_Ruppel_in_Venezuela|access-date=2021-04-22|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422041830/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/215621978_Macrofauna_Associated_with_Echiuran_Burrows_A_Review_with_New_Observations_of_the_Innkeeper_Worm_Ochetostoma_erythrogrammon_Leuckart_and_Ruppel_in_Venezuela|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

单环刺螠分布於[[渤海湾|渤海湾]]與[[日本|日本]]、[[韓國|韓國]]和[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]遠東地區的海域<ref name="pmid24698400"/><ref name=Gong>{{cite journal|title=Genetic diversity and population structure of penis fish (Urechis unicinctus) based on mitochondrial and nuclear gene markers.|journal=Mitochondrial Dna. Part A, DNA Mapping, Sequencing, and Analysis|volume=29|issue=8|pages=1261–1268|pmid=29482423|year=2018|last1=Gong|first1=J.|last2=Zhao|first2=R.|last3=Deng|first3=J.|last4=Zhao|first4=Y.|last5=Zuo|first5=J.|last6=Huang|first6=L.|last7=Jing|first7=M.|doi=10.1080/24701394.2018.1444039}}</ref>，為季節性漁獲，在中國一般在春季捕獲<ref name="food">{{cite web|url=http://tw.people.com.cn/BIG5/14816/14896/910197.html|title=吃在春季的鱉蟹鱔貝|publisher=北京晨報|language=zh-tw|access-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104020526/http://tw.people.com.cn/BIG5/14816/14896/910197.html|archive-date=2016-11-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在日本則在冬季捕獲<ref name="pmid24698400"/>。日本曾有多次發現大量单环刺螠擱淺在沙灘上的紀錄，2012年、2013年的1月至2月曾有大批单环刺螠在夜間擱淺於日本[[宮城縣|宮城縣]]的海灘上，可能與其在夜晚游動、交配有關<ref name="pmid24698400">{{cite journal| author=Abe H, Sato-Okoshi W, Tanaka M, Okoshi K, Teramoto W, Kondoh T | display-authors=etal| title=Swimming behavior of the spoon worm Urechis unicinctus (Annelida, Echiura). | journal=Zoology (Jena) | year= 2014 | volume= 117 | issue= 3 | pages= 216-23 | pmid=24698400 | doi=10.1016/j.zool.2013.12.001 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=24698400  }} </ref>。

单环刺螠對[[硫化物|硫化物]]有較強的耐受與解毒能力，也因此被當作沿海硫化物代謝相關研究的[[模式生物|模式生物]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lunwentianxia.com/product.sf.4078513.1/|title=单环刺螠（Urechis unicinctus）硫醌氧化还原酶的研究|language=zh-cn|access-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718142115/http://lunwentianxia.com/product.sf.4078513.1/|archive-date=2014-07-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==经济价值==
[[File:Haichang.ogv|thumb]][[威海|威海]]一間餐廳中的单环刺螠]]
单环刺螠在[[中國|中國]]、[[日本|日本]]、[[韩國|韩國]]等地（特別是韓國<ref>{{cite news|url=http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20091005/00480_001.html|title=海雲臺惡鯊水中轉|publisher=太陽報|language=zh-hant|access-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100109184128/http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20091005/00480_001.html|archive-date=2010-01-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>）常被生吃<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Choi |first1=Sang-Duk |last2=Kim |first2=Ho-Jin |last3=Rha |first3=Sung-Ju |first4=K. J. |last4=Choe |first5=H. L. |last5=Suh |year=1998 |title=Studies on the commercial scale production of Urechis unicinctus (von Drasche) in southern Korea. |journal=''[[麗水大學論文集|Bulletin of Yosu National University]]'' |volume=13 |issue=2 |pages=pp. 973-981 |issn=1225-8725 |language=ko }}</ref>，其口感脆嫩，被稱作「裸體的[[海參|海參]]」<ref name="xinhua">{{cite news|url=http://www.sd.xinhuanet.com/wq/2010-01/11/content_18739395.htm|title=海腸|publisher=[[新華網|新華網]]|date=2010-01-11|language=zh|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629171032/http://www.sd.xinhuanet.com/wq/2010-01/11/content_18739395.htm|archivedate=2013-06-29|accessdate=2011-12-02}}</ref>配上[[韭菜|韭菜]]清炒的「[[韭菜海腸|韭菜海腸]]」為[[煙台|煙台]]的名菜<ref name="food" />。[[中醫|中醫]]則認為单环刺螠有[[壯陽|壯陽]]、溫補[[肝|肝]][[腎|腎]]的作用，適合男性食用<ref name="xinhua" />。除了食用之外，单环刺螠也常作為[[魚餌|魚餌]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://akko0220.at.webry.info/200504/article_15.html|title=うにょ系食材・海腸|language=ja|access-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304212906/http://akko0220.at.webry.info/200504/article_15.html|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
